IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Holly Joy LEWIS and Eric William Lewis Upon the Petition of Holly Joy Lewis, Petitioner-Appellant/Cross-Appellee, And Concerning Eric William Lewis, Respondent-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 17-1983 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Holly Lewis appeals, and Eric Lewis cross-appeals, the modification of a dissolution-of-marriage decree. AFFIRMED ON APPEAL, AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED ON CROSS-APPEAL, AND REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.

AFFIRMED ON APPEAL. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED ON CROSSAPPEAL. REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.
